hydra-llm (0.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New `hydra-llm addlocal <path>` command. Registers a GGUF you already
    have on disk as a catalog entry without copying it. Auto-derives id,
    file size, and a free default port; flags cover --tier, --ram-gb,
    --vram-gb, --gpu-layers, --port, --id, --name, --family, --license,
    --context, --replace, --yes. With --link, files outside models_dir
    are symlinked in (the engine container only mounts models_dir).
  * docs: rewrite the "Bring your own models" section around addlocal so
    BYO is a one-liner instead of hand-written YAML. Mention addlocal in
    the project page's subcommand list.

